{
  "text": "Several studies have previously reported that weight loss before chemotherapy is associated with poor survival in cancer patients, especially in patients with GC [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . The results of the present study also demonstrated that weight loss of .5% before chemotherapy predicted poor survival in patients with advanced GC.",
